3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper uses deep learning techniques to develop an algorithm for lesion segmentation, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper involves the use of image processing techniques for lesion segmentation, which can be considered a form of information retrieval from images. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with the analysis of skin lesion images, which can be considered a form of multimedia analysis.
